BOOTSTRAP-ICON-PICKER:
----------------------
Github-Link: 
https://victor-valencia.github.io/bootstrap-iconpicker/

CDN:
<link rel="stylesheet" href="dist/css/bootstrap-iconpicker.min.css"/>
<script type="text/javascript" src="dist/js/bootstrap-iconpicker.bundle.min.js"></script>

BLADE:--
Insert:--
<button name="icon"  class="btn btn-primary" role="iconpicker"  id="icon" data-selected-class="btn-danger" data-unselected-class="btn-info" > </button> 
Update:--
<button name="icon" data-icon="{{$category->icon}}"  id="icon"  class="btn btn-primary" role="iconpicker"  data-selected-class="btn-danger" data-unselected-class="btn-info" > </button> 
